{"tid":895675,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：山齊士已失信心 強項都無法發揮出來","createTime":"2018-11-09T11:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T14:07:35.000Z","uid":147522,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f8c64ab14058a380570d240e11453ec987775b","tid":895675,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"　　山齊士自從冬窗加盟曼聯以來一直比較低迷，拿著英超第一週薪，表現卻配不上身價，這讓他遭到了不少非議。山齊士昔日的恩師雲格在接受採訪時也表達了自己的觀點，雲格認為曼聯的山齊士有些失去信心了。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格接受beIN Sports採訪時說：「我覺得山齊士有些失去信心了。他的強項是盤帶和過人。當球員失去信心的時候是最脆弱的。因為比賽中的表現就是基於信心和積極性，他慢慢的失去了這些。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「賽季開始的時候他身體狀況很好，但是之後有些下降。當然摩連奴都雪藏了他一段時間，現在我認為他已經恢復了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　在盧卡古受傷後，山齊士近期都作為曼聯的正選中鋒出戰，表現可圈可點。不過面對祖雲達斯的比賽中，山齊士出現了受傷的狀況。《郵報》的消息稱，還不確定他能否出戰本週末的曼市打吡。"},{"pid":"4d2b90c3444ce1d7c3faf4feab71b6a5da49b584","tid":895675,"uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3AR5JL8R3k8CY/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3AR5JL8R3k8CY%2Fgiphy.gif&h=21511b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爺爺真的太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d036ff4273d93236f7444fd45ded1eb84eb1d6","tid":895675,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ad9074008fed9fbcac91e323d2dce80247c336","tid":895675,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺準備好教返好山齊士了"},{"pid":"b920a6fd223ac7efea5c06b65051c4245d165d10","tid":895675,"uid":55346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2